data.description: WOW! Just minutes from Des Moines. Check out this 3 bed 2 bath home with over an acre of land. This home has been well kept with the same owner for years. Fall in love with the huge spacious heated shop (that does not include the attached 2 stall garage), and fully fenced in backyard! This home has the most beautiful country like views you can only imagine. Call today and schedule your private tour, you will not want to miss what this home has to offer.
